=>Things to Know Before Installing WordPress Before you being the install,There are few things you have to do,
(1)Access to your web server (via shell or FTP)
(2)A text editor
(3)An FTP Client
(4)Your web browser of choice

Download:
=>Download and unzip the WordPress package from http://wordpress.org/download/.
=>You should get backup Orginal your Wordpress site and latest database  backup
=>You should keep in your mind Check new wordpress  compatibility with your old wordpress site plugins before  you  upgrade wordpress site list down plugins compatibility
=>Upload latest wordpress zip folder using ftp/Cpanel
=>Rename wp-admin and wp-include 
=>upload new wp-admin and wp-include  

 
